With the approaching launch of the\nnext-generation X-ray satellite Astro-H, observations of spectral lines with\nunprecedented high resolution will become a reality. Our self-consistent\ncalculations of the X-ray spectra from various progenitors will help interpret\nfuture observations of SNRs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Jul 2014 03:12:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Jul 2014 09:47:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
